1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:11,160
 Mi smo ovdje radi dva razloga. Prvi je razlog da bi smo došli u kontakt s Bogom,

2
00:00:11,160 --> 00:00:20,660
 drugi rečimo da bi nas Bog izliječio i oslobodio. A drugi razlog je o tome da bi smo došli u kontakt s drugim ljudima.

3
00:00:20,660 --> 00:00:28,500
 Ako hoćeš ozdraviti do kraja, onda nije dosta sam lići k Bogu i moliti ga da te ozdravi,

4
00:00:28,500 --> 00:00:33,360
 nego moraš početi voljeti druge da bi ozdravio.

5
00:00:33,360 --> 00:00:39,900
 Mi u agioterapiji imamo jednu posebnu terapiju. Zove se Agape terapija.

6
00:00:39,900 --> 00:00:49,040
 To je terapija Božanskom ljubavlju gdje pacijent upija Božju bezuvjetnu ljubav i nježnost.

7
00:00:49,040 --> 00:00:52,260
 I dok upija, on se liječi.

8
00:00:52,260 --> 00:00:57,000
 Međutim, taj lijek ne može ostati, to zdravlje ne može učvrstiti.

9
00:00:57,000 --> 00:01:00,240
 Nekod pacijent sada ne počne voljeti druge.

10
00:01:01,860 --> 00:01:06,600
 Jer nije ljubav samo u tome da te netko voli,

11
00:01:06,600 --> 00:01:11,620
 nego da nakon toga što te netko voli, ti počneš voljeti nekog drugoga.

12
00:01:13,720 --> 00:01:19,160
 Ljubav naime je samo do pola u tebi ako tebe samo netko voli.

13
00:01:19,160 --> 00:01:23,760
 A ljubavlju se potpuno ispunjaš kad ti nekoga voliš.

14
00:01:23,760 --> 00:01:31,700
 Jer kad tebe netko voli onda si siguran, onda se osjećaš ta ti je egzistencija sigurno.

15
00:01:31,700 --> 00:01:35,200
 Kad znaš da te Bog voli, onda znaš siguran se bit će sve dobro.

16
00:01:35,200 --> 00:01:42,120
 Ali ima bezbroj ljudi koji tebi trebaju, gdje tvoje srce čezne za njima, gdje bih tio s njima razgovarati,

17
00:01:42,220 --> 00:01:43,940
 Htio bi im pomoć, htio bi biti uz njih.

18
00:01:43,940 --> 00:01:49,960
 I ako nikoga ne voliš, osjećaš se frustriranim i besmislenim.

19
00:01:49,960 --> 00:01:55,500
 Drugim rječima, Božja ljubav ulazi u tebe i voli te,

20
00:01:55,500 --> 00:01:58,960
 ali ti još ne transcendiraš, još ne nadilaziš sebe.

21
00:01:58,960 --> 00:02:05,060
 Kad počneš ljubiti drugog, tad si nadišao sebe, tad si zaboravio sebe i tad postaješ zdrav.

22
00:02:09,380 --> 00:02:13,160
 Bezbrojni su ljudi koji ne mogu opraštati drugima. Zašto?

23
00:02:13,160 --> 00:02:19,300
 Zato što neprestano upijaju Božju ljubav i stano traže da ih netko voli.

24
00:02:19,300 --> 00:02:23,120
 A oni nisu nikada počeli voljeti druge.

25
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:33,100
 Jer u tebe se izlije neka ljepota, nešto duboko i snažno i neka nježnost,

26
00:02:33,100 --> 00:02:36,120
 onda kad nekoga voliš. Sjetiš i samo kad vidiš malo djete,

27
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:38,200
 pa kad ga zagrliš, pa ga počneš ljubiti.

28
00:02:39,380 --> 00:02:43,360
 Pa vodiš ga na ruku, a ono, djete, klikće, a tvoje srce igra.

29
00:02:43,360 --> 00:02:46,920
 I ako ti toga ne imaš, ti onda ne osjećaš ljubav.

30
00:02:46,920 --> 00:02:52,200
 Kad roditelji samo vole djete,

31
00:02:52,200 --> 00:02:55,600
 neizmjerno ga vole i razmazde ga,

32
00:02:55,600 --> 00:02:57,320
 to znači vežu uz sebe,

33
00:02:57,320 --> 00:02:59,500
 tada djete postaje bolesto.

34
00:02:59,500 --> 00:03:01,480
 Ne samo duhoru, nego i psihički.

35
00:03:03,160 --> 00:03:06,380
 jer djete vapi da nekoga i ono voli.

36
00:03:06,380 --> 00:03:09,120
 Da ide k drugima.

37
00:03:09,120 --> 00:03:15,740
 Jer ako imate punu čašu, onda je čaša nesretna što ima tko popiti.

38
00:03:18,140 --> 00:03:20,300
 Kad imaš čokoladu, pa i sam pojedeš,

39
00:03:20,300 --> 00:03:22,500
 to je najveća nesrća što ti se može dogoditi.

40
00:03:22,500 --> 00:03:26,000
 A kad ti nju podijeliš, ona je stostruko slađa.

41
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:27,600
 Probajte, pa ćete vidjeti.

42
00:03:30,720 --> 00:03:31,820
 Zašto je to tako?

43
00:03:31,820 --> 00:03:35,580
 Pa shvatite, zato što je čovjek stvoren na sliku Božu.

44
00:03:35,580 --> 00:03:39,640
 A slika Boža je da Bog nije jedan i sam,

45
00:03:39,640 --> 00:03:42,200
 nego jedan u trojici.

46
00:03:42,200 --> 00:03:45,500
 To su tri osobe koje se vole ludo.

47
00:03:45,500 --> 00:03:50,700
 Prema tome, jer čovjek na tu sliku ne može drugačije nego voljeti.

48
00:03:50,700 --> 00:03:54,480
 I on je nesretan i bolestan dok nekoga ne voli.

49
00:03:57,760 --> 00:04:03,060
 I zašto smo rekli onda da tko ne oprašta neće nikad postati zdrav,

50
00:04:03,060 --> 00:04:04,200
 čak ni fizički.

51
00:04:04,200 --> 00:04:06,080
 Upravo zato.

52
00:04:06,080 --> 00:04:10,000
 Dok ti nekom ne opraštaš, ti će imati dovoljno razloga

53
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:12,420
 da ti se ni jedan čovjek ne svidi.

54
00:04:12,420 --> 00:04:18,960
 Tek kad počneš opraštati zato što ti se ne sviđaju ljudi,

55
00:04:18,960 --> 00:04:20,320
 što ti nisu simpatični.

56
00:04:20,320 --> 00:04:23,720
 Kad počneš opraštati, od jedan puta ćeš ti se pogled otvoriti

57
00:04:23,720 --> 00:04:25,700
 za ono vječno, duboko u ljudima,

58
00:04:25,700 --> 00:04:27,660
 zaljubit ćeš se u svakog čovjeka,

59
00:04:27,660 --> 00:04:28,740
 osobito u siromaka,

60
00:04:28,740 --> 00:04:34,540
 osobito u jadnog pijanca koji sad prljavi kakav sve ne.

61
00:04:34,540 --> 00:04:37,680
 Zaljubit ćeš se da ćeš vijeti nego u dušu iznutra.

62
00:04:37,680 --> 00:04:40,840
 I tad kad zavoliš dušu, tad oseće da si sretan.

63
00:04:40,840 --> 00:04:42,020
 Tad počinje nebo.

64
00:04:45,120 --> 00:04:47,360
 Bezbroj ljudi idu u molitvene grupe,

65
00:04:47,360 --> 00:04:49,060
 idu na sve moguće seminare,

66
00:04:49,060 --> 00:04:51,880
 obavljaju duhone vježbe,

67
00:04:51,880 --> 00:04:58,280
 a uvijek su jednako nesretni, frustrirani,

68
00:04:58,280 --> 00:05:00,060
 besmisleni, jadni.

69
00:05:03,160 --> 00:05:06,420
 Ima ljudi koji idu svake nedelje i svaki dan na misu,

70
00:05:06,420 --> 00:05:08,680
 ali ništa, ni koraka nisu krenuti.

71
00:05:08,680 --> 00:05:09,580
 Čim mi izađu s mise,

72
00:05:09,580 --> 00:05:12,200
 ta, ta, ta, ta, ogovor, ogovor, ogovor.

73
00:05:13,740 --> 00:05:14,520
 Jer si glavno susjed,

74
00:05:14,520 --> 00:05:15,380
 daj svi ide ovog župnika,

75
00:05:15,380 --> 00:05:16,980
 oj kakav ja, pa kak se danas obuka,

76
00:05:16,980 --> 00:05:18,260
 pa gled kako ono priše nos,

77
00:05:18,260 --> 00:05:19,740
 pa svi ide kakav mu frizura danas stoji.

78
00:05:19,740 --> 00:05:21,140
 I gotovo je.

79
00:05:21,140 --> 00:05:27,260
 Jer svaka negativna pomisa o tebe dijeli od drugih ljudi.

80
00:05:27,260 --> 00:05:31,100
 I to ne samo da se dijeliš od župnika,

81
00:05:31,100 --> 00:05:32,060
 što se njega kritizira,

82
00:05:32,060 --> 00:05:33,080
 no da se dijeliš i od vjernika,

83
00:05:33,080 --> 00:05:34,200
 da više nikom ne možeš poglatožiti,

84
00:05:34,200 --> 00:05:35,040
 sad si ti ljud,

85
00:05:35,040 --> 00:05:37,720
 jer u tebi zlo i negativnost i mrak.

86
00:05:42,120 --> 00:05:45,540
 Zato nemoguće je bilo koga zavoljeti da mu ne praštaš.

87
00:05:45,540 --> 00:05:49,000
 Kad praštaš, ti dopuštaš njemu da dođe k tebi,

88
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:50,960
 tad ga vidiš izbliza i tada ga zavoliš

89
00:05:50,960 --> 00:05:54,560
 i tada si prešao zapravo granicu ljudskoga.

90
00:05:54,560 --> 00:05:57,020
 Tad si sa zemaljskog ušao na nebesko.

91
00:05:57,020 --> 00:05:59,100
 Tad si od ljudskog ušao na božansko.

92
00:05:59,100 --> 00:06:02,680
 Tada si sretan i tad postaješ zdrav.

93
00:06:02,680 --> 00:06:07,180
 To je opasno ste uvijek i hagioterapije,

94
00:06:07,180 --> 00:06:10,800
 pogotovo hagioterapeuta ako ne zna tu bitnu činjenicu,

95
00:06:11,300 --> 00:06:13,820
 pa ako stalno, stalno napaja ljude božom ljubavu,

96
00:06:13,820 --> 00:06:15,580
 božom ljubavu i vidi da ne uspjeva,

97
00:06:15,580 --> 00:06:16,640
 neće daći daleko.

98
00:06:16,640 --> 00:06:20,260
 Ti moraš pacijentu isto vremeno pomoći,

99
00:06:20,260 --> 00:06:22,040
 jednak počne nekoga voljeti.

100
00:06:22,040 --> 00:06:24,580
 Dok mu dadeš samo malo ljubavi,

101
00:06:24,580 --> 00:06:26,140
 sad ju nauči, idi praštati.

102
00:06:26,140 --> 00:06:28,120
 Možeš li voljeti majku,

103
00:06:28,120 --> 00:06:29,380
 možeš voljeti oca,

104
00:06:29,380 --> 00:06:30,400
 možeš ovoga ili onoga.

105
00:06:34,120 --> 00:06:36,460
 Tek kad počneš voljeti nekoga bit će zdrav.

106
00:06:36,460 --> 00:06:36,820
 Zašto?

107
00:06:36,900 --> 00:06:40,800
 Dok nego ti ne oprašaš i ne voliš onoga koji tebe mrzi,

108
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:43,760
 dota će taj ispijati sve tvoje snage.

109
00:06:43,760 --> 00:06:48,080
 Poznam ljude koji u obitelji ne mogu trpjeti svoju,

110
00:06:48,080 --> 00:06:51,180
 ni oca, ni majku, ni sestru, ni nikoga.

111
00:06:51,180 --> 00:06:51,600
 Zašto?

112
00:06:53,080 --> 00:06:55,860
 Ti uvijek prigovara, uvijek ti neko prigovara.

113
00:06:55,860 --> 00:06:57,660
 Prigovori ti sesa, prigovori žena,

114
00:06:57,660 --> 00:06:59,440
 prigovori djete, prigovori punica,

115
00:06:59,440 --> 00:07:00,400
 prigovori sve krva.

116
00:07:00,400 --> 00:07:02,660
 I oni su nesretni, šta rade?

117
00:07:02,660 --> 00:07:06,420
 Prestano se dijele, idemo mužu od ove moje sve krve,

118
00:07:06,420 --> 00:07:07,880
 to više ne može se.

119
00:07:07,880 --> 00:07:10,240
 Idemo ženo od ove lude punice, ne može izdržati.

120
00:07:10,240 --> 00:07:14,280
 I ti moraš se, ideš, bježi, bježi, bježi.

121
00:07:14,280 --> 00:07:16,020
 Idemo od majke, ne mogu već to trpjeti,

122
00:07:16,020 --> 00:07:16,780
 stalno me opominje.

123
00:07:16,780 --> 00:07:18,320
 Idemo te sestre poludile.

124
00:07:19,540 --> 00:07:21,620
 Tu nije rješenje, prijatelji dragi.

125
00:07:21,620 --> 00:07:24,340
 Idemo se rastaviti u braku, ne mogu više s tobom.

126
00:07:24,340 --> 00:07:25,460
 Tu nije rješenje.

127
00:07:25,460 --> 00:07:27,740
 Samo ćeš biti još bolesniji.

128
00:07:27,740 --> 00:07:29,780
 To je jedna bolest i rana na drugu.

129
00:07:29,780 --> 00:07:33,080
 Ne samo da se ne prestano opominjate,

130
00:07:33,080 --> 00:07:34,640
 da li prestano se kritizirate,

131
00:07:34,640 --> 00:07:37,840
 da li prestano se sukobljavate, ranjavate, traumatizirate,

132
00:07:37,840 --> 00:07:41,260
 nego sad još odlazite i sad tek nastaje neizlječiva rana.

133
00:07:41,260 --> 00:07:43,520
 Tek sad ste bolesti, najdublje.

134
00:07:48,180 --> 00:07:50,620
 Bezbrojni ljudi, pogotovo jer dođe mi zlo,

135
00:07:50,620 --> 00:07:52,200
 kad još kakviju terapeuti i počem govoriti,

136
00:07:52,200 --> 00:07:54,620
 pa rastavite se, šta ćete vidjeti da ne možete izdržati,

137
00:07:54,620 --> 00:07:55,320
 to je najgore.

138
00:07:55,320 --> 00:07:57,400
 Ti me ne liječiš više pacijenta.

139
00:07:57,400 --> 00:08:01,460
 Ti moraš od njega zahvati od tog pacijenta,

140
00:08:01,460 --> 00:08:03,300
 da on polako, polako uhvati od roda.

141
00:08:03,300 --> 00:08:06,000
 Samo osjeti, znam dubine ovoga čovjeka

142
00:08:06,000 --> 00:08:07,000
 koji me mrazi mene vole.

143
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:08,280
 I ti si se spasio.

144
00:08:08,280 --> 00:08:09,960
 Dubine njegove me vole.

145
00:08:09,960 --> 00:08:13,080
 I drugo, opraštam ti, jer te razumijem.

146
00:08:15,240 --> 00:08:16,340
 Nisam nija bolji.

147
00:08:16,340 --> 00:08:18,100
 Ja tebe kritiziram.

148
00:08:18,100 --> 00:08:20,460
 Opraštam ti, opraštam, opraštam.

149
00:08:20,460 --> 00:08:23,020
 Tad si nadišao sebe,

150
00:08:23,020 --> 00:08:24,280
 tad si nadišao zlo,

151
00:08:24,280 --> 00:08:25,900
 tad te zlo više ne pogađa,

152
00:08:25,900 --> 00:08:26,960
 jer si više iznad njega.

153
00:08:26,960 --> 00:08:29,140
 Tad ljubiš i tad si u nebu.

154
00:08:29,140 --> 00:08:30,340
 Tad si sličan Bogu.

155
00:08:33,460 --> 00:08:38,120
 Ne postoji mogućnost da se izliječiš u svojoj duhovnoj duši.

156
00:08:38,120 --> 00:08:41,580
 U svojoj, u sebi kao osobi,

157
00:08:41,580 --> 00:08:43,800
 a da ne počneš voljeti druge.

158
00:08:43,800 --> 00:08:48,120
 Zato Isusa koji je htio pomoć čovjeku,

159
00:08:48,120 --> 00:08:49,380
 nije mogo drugačije nego da kaže

160
00:08:49,380 --> 00:08:51,360
 ljubite svoje neprijatelje.

161
00:08:51,360 --> 00:08:54,560
 Dokle go ti mrziš neprijatelja,

162
00:08:54,560 --> 00:08:55,880
 on tebe ranjava.

163
00:08:55,880 --> 00:08:58,120
 Jer neprijatelj nije unaj koji te na kraju

164
00:08:58,120 --> 00:09:00,940
 sa kaljačnikovim ubija

165
00:09:00,940 --> 00:09:02,560
 i koji, ne znam kakve,

166
00:09:02,560 --> 00:09:04,220
 mine i granate baca na tebe.

167
00:09:04,220 --> 00:09:05,480
 Nije to, to je ono kranje,

168
00:09:05,480 --> 00:09:06,600
 to ubije malo tvoje tijelo,

169
00:09:06,600 --> 00:09:07,180
 to nije opasno.

170
00:09:07,180 --> 00:09:09,240
 On tebe ubija već time što ti je neprijatelj.

171
00:09:09,240 --> 00:09:10,940
 On može biti danas u kini tvoj neprijatelj.

172
00:09:10,940 --> 00:09:12,700
 Tebe muči, tu su granate,

173
00:09:12,700 --> 00:09:13,440
 u tebe muči.

174
00:09:13,440 --> 00:09:14,700
 Nemoj mi ga spominjati,

175
00:09:14,700 --> 00:09:16,480
 užasaj, ne mogu govoriti o njemu.

176
00:09:16,480 --> 00:09:17,580
 Ili ćeš početi govoriti o njemu,

177
00:09:17,580 --> 00:09:19,280
 i vidiš, tvoje vrti, vrti, vrti.

178
00:09:19,280 --> 00:09:20,980
 Tvoja savjesta je izranjena,

179
00:09:21,100 --> 00:09:22,240
 tvoje srce je izranjeno,

180
00:09:22,240 --> 00:09:23,920
 tvoji želuda stvara

181
00:09:23,920 --> 00:09:24,880
 sve moguće

182
00:09:24,880 --> 00:09:29,420
 sve moguće čireve.

183
00:09:29,420 --> 00:09:30,220
 Gotov si.

184
00:09:30,220 --> 00:09:32,520
 Stvar je tako jasno.

185
00:09:32,520 --> 00:09:35,160
 I nemamo drugog puta

186
00:09:35,160 --> 00:09:36,100
 nego početi ljubiti.

187
00:09:36,100 --> 00:09:40,780
 Ali shvatite, ljubav je uvijek

188
00:09:40,780 --> 00:09:42,780
 dvostruka, najprije pasivna.

189
00:09:42,780 --> 00:09:44,840
 Najprije te ljubav rađa.

190
00:09:44,840 --> 00:09:46,440
 Primaš ljubav najprije.

191
00:09:46,440 --> 00:09:49,060
 Bog me voli, to je bitno.

192
00:09:49,060 --> 00:09:50,800
 Ako toga nemaš, nećeš nikad početi

193
00:09:50,800 --> 00:09:52,080
 ljubiti, ne možeš ljubiti.

194
00:09:52,080 --> 00:09:53,700
 Jer tebe nema.

195
00:09:53,700 --> 00:09:56,800
 Najprije te Božja ljubav preporodi.

196
00:09:56,800 --> 00:09:59,720
 Ali ta ljubav sad može o sad,

197
00:09:59,720 --> 00:10:01,060
 sad ti ideš ljubiti,

198
00:10:01,060 --> 00:10:02,080
 sad tom ljubavljom.

199
00:10:02,080 --> 00:10:03,260
 Sad si siguran.

200
00:10:03,260 --> 00:10:05,020
 I sad te više niko ne može raniti.

201
00:10:05,020 --> 00:10:06,500
 I sad si slobodan.

202
00:10:06,500 --> 00:10:09,880
 Koliko mi ljudi dolazi,

203
00:10:09,880 --> 00:10:10,720
 pa šta da radim,

204
00:10:10,720 --> 00:10:12,100
 pa ja to ne mogu više izdršati ovo,

205
00:10:12,100 --> 00:10:12,660
 kažem pa.

206
00:10:12,660 --> 00:10:14,900
 I šta ćeš sad?

207
00:10:14,900 --> 00:10:17,840
 Pa najrednji bi pobjegao.

208
00:10:17,840 --> 00:10:18,500
 Pobjegni i?

209
00:10:20,500 --> 00:10:22,440
 Sad ćeš da ti bježiš zajedno sa svojim neprijateljom.

210
00:10:22,440 --> 00:10:23,060
 On je u tebi.

211
00:10:23,060 --> 00:10:27,480
 Nijedan neprijatelj nije izvan tebe.

212
00:10:27,480 --> 00:10:28,520
 Nemaš kamo pobjeći.

213
00:10:28,520 --> 00:10:30,720
 Bježi samo da te fizički ne rani.

214
00:10:30,720 --> 00:10:33,280
 Ali on doliko gore ono što te on iznutra već,

215
00:10:33,280 --> 00:10:34,120
 ranjava, ranjava,

216
00:10:34,120 --> 00:10:34,740
 redi to dalje,

217
00:10:34,740 --> 00:10:35,320
 traje.

218
00:10:35,320 --> 00:10:36,780
 Nemaš kamo pobjeći.

219
00:10:37,780 --> 00:10:38,680
 Rasta ove brakovi,

220
00:10:38,680 --> 00:10:39,540
 užani si sa drugom.

221
00:10:39,540 --> 00:10:42,120
 Ma kak je ona žena od prije koju si ostavio mučite?

222
00:10:42,120 --> 00:10:43,640
 Ona je u tebi čoveče.

223
00:10:43,640 --> 00:10:46,460
 Tva savjez je nagrižena i nestaje mu.

224
00:10:46,460 --> 00:10:47,660
 Užas ne hvata.

225
00:10:47,660 --> 00:10:50,020
 Prema tome,

226
00:10:50,020 --> 00:10:51,880
 rješenje problema je samo

227
00:10:51,880 --> 00:10:54,100
 nadići to,

228
00:10:54,100 --> 00:10:54,960
 početvoljiti,

229
00:10:54,960 --> 00:10:56,140
 oprostiti

230
00:10:56,140 --> 00:10:58,560
 i vidjeti da

231
00:10:58,560 --> 00:11:00,740
 dubina u svakom čovjeku

232
00:11:00,740 --> 00:11:01,340
 su s tobom

233
00:11:01,340 --> 00:11:03,600
 u savjezu.

234
00:11:03,600 --> 00:11:06,100
 I možeš izliječiti svakog čovjeka.

235
00:11:06,100 --> 00:11:07,460
 Prema tome,

236
00:11:07,460 --> 00:11:10,920
 nije rješenje da bježiš od zla i od ljudi,

237
00:11:10,920 --> 00:11:12,280
 nego da zlo prihvatiš

238
00:11:12,280 --> 00:11:13,200
 i da ga pobjediš.

239
00:11:13,200 --> 00:11:16,340
 Nije u tome da tražiš od drugi

240
00:11:16,340 --> 00:11:16,900
 nek se mijenja.

241
00:11:16,900 --> 00:11:18,300
 Moja žena me stalno kaže

242
00:11:18,300 --> 00:11:19,640
 napadaj, više to ne mogu.

243
00:11:19,640 --> 00:11:20,660
 Ako se ona ne promijeni,

244
00:11:20,660 --> 00:11:21,600
 rekao šta što onda?

245
00:11:21,600 --> 00:11:23,800
 Ako se promijeri,

246
00:11:23,800 --> 00:11:25,560
 to nije biti ništa zdraviji ni bolji.

247
00:11:26,140 --> 00:11:28,340
 jer u tebi je zlo.

248
00:11:28,340 --> 00:11:30,480
 Pa šta da napravim?

249
00:11:30,480 --> 00:11:32,140
 Promijeni se ti prema njoj.

250
00:11:32,140 --> 00:11:33,040
 A, dosta mi je.

251
00:11:33,040 --> 00:11:34,640
 Dobro, onda kad je dosta,

252
00:11:34,640 --> 00:11:34,860
 idi.

253
00:11:34,860 --> 00:11:36,460
 Pa kao je tu ispred tebe.

254
00:11:36,460 --> 00:11:37,500
 Samo skoči.

255
00:11:37,500 --> 00:11:42,440
 To drugo treba učiti,

256
00:11:42,440 --> 00:11:43,400
 prijatelji dragi.

257
00:11:43,400 --> 00:11:48,500
 Jer mi se možemo sastaviti ovde

258
00:11:48,500 --> 00:11:49,920
 još stotinu godina.

259
00:11:49,920 --> 00:11:51,420
 Dok ne napravimo zajednice,

260
00:11:51,420 --> 00:11:52,840
 dok mi ne budemo zajednice,

261
00:11:52,840 --> 00:11:54,080
 znači zajednice,

262
00:11:54,080 --> 00:11:55,280
 dok ti ne zavoliš neke ljude

263
00:11:55,280 --> 00:11:56,100
 koji dolaze ovde,

264
00:11:56,140 --> 00:11:57,260
 ti uzalu dolaziš.

265
00:11:57,260 --> 00:12:01,360
 A zajedni šta?

266
00:12:01,360 --> 00:12:02,060
 Nije u tom da kažeš

267
00:12:02,060 --> 00:12:02,820
 joj prvo se bračiće,

268
00:12:02,820 --> 00:12:03,720
 lijepo nam govori.

269
00:12:03,720 --> 00:12:05,380
 Joj, fin, osjećam se tako,

270
00:12:05,380 --> 00:12:06,260
 blaži dušu.

271
00:12:06,260 --> 00:12:07,380
 Da, i onda kad izađeš van,

272
00:12:07,380 --> 00:12:08,960
 neputa naletiš opet na one

273
00:12:08,960 --> 00:12:11,620
 koji ti odblažuju dušu.

274
00:12:11,620 --> 00:12:12,680
 Koji te raje,

275
00:12:12,680 --> 00:12:13,920
 a joj, Ivančić,

276
00:12:13,920 --> 00:12:15,120
 u mojoj ništvinici napravi,

277
00:12:15,120 --> 00:12:15,640
 opet ja.

278
00:12:18,140 --> 00:12:24,220
 ljubiti to dvostruko znači,

279
00:12:24,220 --> 00:12:25,660
 voljen sam,

280
00:12:25,660 --> 00:12:27,420
 ja imam pravo živjeti,

281
00:12:27,420 --> 00:12:28,880
 a voljen sam znači,

282
00:12:28,880 --> 00:12:30,240
 nisam ugrožen,

283
00:12:30,240 --> 00:12:31,620
 ja se ne bojim,

284
00:12:32,620 --> 00:12:33,960
 mene niko ne može ugroziti.

285
00:12:33,960 --> 00:12:35,180
 Ja se ne bojim,

286
00:12:35,180 --> 00:12:35,800
 ja se ne bojim.

287
00:12:35,800 --> 00:12:37,660
 Mene je Bog ludo voli.

288
00:12:37,660 --> 00:12:39,740
 A Bog je apsolutno samodobar.

289
00:12:39,740 --> 00:12:41,140
 I u tome najprije moraš se

290
00:12:41,140 --> 00:12:42,560
 otopiti, uživati,

291
00:12:42,560 --> 00:12:43,260
 roditi se.

292
00:12:43,260 --> 00:12:45,040
 Kada si ukadi i uživaš

293
00:12:45,040 --> 00:12:45,880
 u Bože ljubavi?

294
00:12:45,880 --> 00:12:46,820
 To najprije moraš.

295
00:12:46,820 --> 00:12:47,700
 Natopiti se moraš,

296
00:12:47,700 --> 00:12:48,820
 balzamirati,

297
00:12:48,820 --> 00:12:50,720
 amalgamirati jednostavno u sebi,

298
00:12:50,720 --> 00:12:51,340
 natopiti,

299
00:12:51,340 --> 00:12:52,860
 prožeti se jednostavno

300
00:12:52,860 --> 00:12:53,460
 Božom ljubavi.

301
00:12:53,460 --> 00:12:55,300
 E sad kad je to proželo,

302
00:12:55,300 --> 00:12:56,420
 sad gledate,

303
00:12:56,420 --> 00:12:57,320
 možeš li voljeti?

304
00:12:57,320 --> 00:12:58,000
 Ako ne možeš,

305
00:12:58,000 --> 00:12:58,300
 onda kažeš,

306
00:12:58,340 --> 00:12:59,100
 joj Bože, još malo.

307
00:12:59,100 --> 00:13:01,100
 Napiješ još jednu čašu

308
00:13:01,100 --> 00:13:01,700
 o njegove ljubavi.

309
00:13:01,700 --> 00:13:02,280
 Sad ide.

310
00:13:02,280 --> 00:13:04,460
 Joj, još malo.

311
00:13:04,460 --> 00:13:06,920
 Je, sad mogu da iso.

312
00:13:06,920 --> 00:13:07,640
 Kako ste?

313
00:13:07,640 --> 00:13:09,560
 Onda počneš,

314
00:13:09,560 --> 00:13:10,860
 tebe volim i tebe volim.

315
00:13:10,860 --> 00:13:12,220
 Gledaš, joj ona me gnjavi.

316
00:13:12,220 --> 00:13:13,140
 Joj, baš te volim.

317
00:13:13,140 --> 00:13:14,240
 I ona mi je gadan.

318
00:13:14,240 --> 00:13:15,000
 Baš me volim.

319
00:13:15,000 --> 00:13:15,960
 Ona nesimpatičan.

320
00:13:15,960 --> 00:13:17,060
 Što mi je drag.

321
00:13:17,060 --> 00:13:17,480
 Dođi.

322
00:13:17,480 --> 00:13:23,760
 I ona ljubiš ježeve,

323
00:13:23,760 --> 00:13:24,400
 kažu ljudi.

324
00:13:24,400 --> 00:13:27,440
 Možeš ježa poljubiti bez brige.

325
00:13:28,300 --> 00:13:29,100
 Ne bode više.

326
00:13:29,100 --> 00:13:33,800
 Hajdemo na taj put.

327
00:13:33,800 --> 00:13:36,140
 Idemo na prvi korak.

328
00:13:36,140 --> 00:13:39,260
 Napunit se Bože ljubavi.

329
00:13:39,260 --> 00:13:41,460
 Pustiti Isusa u tebe

330
00:13:41,460 --> 00:13:42,100
 da te ljubi.

331
00:13:42,100 --> 00:13:44,160
 Jeste vi zapamtili

332
00:13:44,160 --> 00:13:45,680
 koji su ono šest točaka

333
00:13:45,680 --> 00:13:47,440
 molitve da biste mogli?

334
00:13:47,440 --> 00:13:48,920
 Jeste zbilja?

335
00:13:48,920 --> 00:13:51,120
 Prva točka, dakle,

336
00:13:51,120 --> 00:13:53,520
 odluči se da hoćeš biti zbogom,

337
00:13:53,520 --> 00:13:54,240
 da hođeš moliti.

338
00:13:54,240 --> 00:13:54,680
 To je prvo.

339
00:13:58,260 --> 00:14:07,600
 Drugo, stani

340
00:14:07,600 --> 00:14:09,140
 na razinu duha.

341
00:14:09,140 --> 00:14:10,680
 Na onu razinu

342
00:14:10,680 --> 00:14:11,820
 gdje si ti kao čovjek

343
00:14:11,820 --> 00:14:12,980
 od Boga stvoren

344
00:14:12,980 --> 00:14:14,140
 na sliku Bože.

345
00:14:14,140 --> 00:14:15,640
 Podsjeti se

346
00:14:15,640 --> 00:14:16,260
 tko si.

347
00:14:19,060 --> 00:14:20,520
 od Boga izlaziš,

348
00:14:20,520 --> 00:14:21,800
 k Bogu ideš.

349
00:14:21,800 --> 00:14:24,280
 U Bogu zavisi

350
00:14:24,280 --> 00:14:25,500
 cijeli tvoj život.

351
00:14:25,500 --> 00:14:27,220
 Tvoja sudbina

352
00:14:27,220 --> 00:14:28,120
 u njegovim rukama.

353
00:14:34,400 --> 00:14:35,960
 I sad na toj razini

354
00:14:35,960 --> 00:14:36,760
 duha načini

355
00:14:36,760 --> 00:14:37,740
 znak križa.

356
00:14:37,740 --> 00:14:39,300
 Prije tom troje,

357
00:14:39,300 --> 00:14:39,760
 misliš,

358
00:14:39,760 --> 00:14:41,000
 to je Isusov križ.

359
00:14:41,000 --> 00:14:42,460
 To mene oslobađa.

360
00:14:42,460 --> 00:14:43,620
 To je presjeto

361
00:14:43,620 --> 00:14:44,440
 trojstvo na meni.

362
00:14:56,860 --> 00:14:57,360
 Dobro,

363
00:14:57,360 --> 00:14:58,160
 ga činom dobro

364
00:14:58,160 --> 00:14:59,180
 pravite znak križa.

365
00:14:59,180 --> 00:15:00,440
 Neki malo požurjem

366
00:15:00,440 --> 00:15:01,320
 sa svim to svetogamen,

367
00:15:01,320 --> 00:15:01,880
 onda to nije.

368
00:15:01,880 --> 00:15:02,900
 Baš je važno

369
00:15:02,900 --> 00:15:03,780
 meditativno.

370
00:15:03,780 --> 00:15:04,860
 Baš nako polako

371
00:15:04,860 --> 00:15:05,580
 u ime Otca

372
00:15:05,580 --> 00:15:07,420
 i Sina

373
00:15:07,420 --> 00:15:09,900
 i Duha

374
00:15:09,900 --> 00:15:11,780
 Svetoga.

375
00:15:11,780 --> 00:15:15,080
 Tada osjetiš da duša,

376
00:15:15,080 --> 00:15:16,060
 jer duša ne može

377
00:15:16,060 --> 00:15:16,860
 tako brzo

378
00:15:16,860 --> 00:15:17,780
 kao tvoja ruka,

379
00:15:17,780 --> 00:15:18,280
 veći duša

380
00:15:18,280 --> 00:15:19,160
 treba malo vremena

381
00:15:19,160 --> 00:15:19,820
 da doživi

382
00:15:19,820 --> 00:15:20,720
 to što ti

383
00:15:20,720 --> 00:15:21,720
 stavljaš na sebe.

384
00:15:21,720 --> 00:15:22,880
 I onda se ispuni

385
00:15:22,880 --> 00:15:24,220
 čitavim

386
00:15:24,220 --> 00:15:25,700
 sadržajem

387
00:15:25,700 --> 00:15:26,720
 znaka križa.

388
00:15:26,720 --> 00:15:32,300
 Četvrta točka.

389
00:15:32,300 --> 00:15:34,940
 Otvori Isusu vratare.

390
00:15:35,100 --> 00:15:36,000
 Isuse, dođi

391
00:15:36,000 --> 00:15:36,880
 slobodno križa.

392
00:15:36,880 --> 00:15:51,640
 Otvorio si mu.

393
00:15:51,640 --> 00:15:54,680
 I sada kao najboljeg prijatelja

394
00:15:54,680 --> 00:15:55,320
 možeš ga pustiti

395
00:15:55,320 --> 00:15:56,240
 u sve odaje,

396
00:15:56,240 --> 00:15:57,220
 u sve prostore

397
00:15:57,220 --> 00:15:57,860
 svoje duše

398
00:15:57,860 --> 00:15:58,560
 i svoga života.

399
00:15:58,560 --> 00:15:59,280
 Rekneš mu Isuse,

400
00:15:59,280 --> 00:16:00,040
 molim te dođi,

401
00:16:00,040 --> 00:16:00,580
 pogledaj.

402
00:16:00,580 --> 00:16:02,700
 Izliječi ono što je ranjeno,

403
00:16:02,700 --> 00:16:04,260
 oprosti ono što je prljavo

404
00:16:04,260 --> 00:16:05,180
 i grešno.

405
00:16:05,180 --> 00:16:08,840
 Budi u meni Isusa.

406
00:16:08,840 --> 00:16:09,760
 Ti samo gledaj

407
00:16:09,760 --> 00:16:10,540
 kako Isus

408
00:16:10,540 --> 00:16:11,260
 mijenja

409
00:16:11,260 --> 00:16:12,380
 tvoju nutrinju.

410
00:16:12,380 --> 00:16:14,220
 Tvoje misli,

411
00:16:14,220 --> 00:16:14,840
 osjećaje,

412
00:16:14,840 --> 00:16:15,920
 doživljaje,

413
00:16:15,920 --> 00:16:17,160
 cijelu tvoju prošlosti.

414
00:16:17,160 --> 00:16:18,960
 Sve tvoje strahove.

415
00:16:18,960 --> 00:16:21,060
 Isus sve pregledava

416
00:16:21,060 --> 00:16:21,300
 i kaže,

417
00:16:21,300 --> 00:16:22,260
 ovo ćemo urediti,

418
00:16:22,260 --> 00:16:22,780
 ovo ćemo.

419
00:16:22,940 --> 00:16:24,640
 Isus pravi u tebi red.

420
00:16:24,640 --> 00:16:32,980
 I peto je onda zagrli mu noge

421
00:16:32,980 --> 00:16:33,760
 i reci Isuse,

422
00:16:33,760 --> 00:16:35,060
 ostane sa mnom.

423
00:16:35,060 --> 00:16:38,540
 Sve će biti dobro.

424
00:16:40,980 --> 00:16:42,180
 nemoj više nikada

425
00:16:42,180 --> 00:16:43,220
 od mene otići.

426
00:16:43,220 --> 00:16:47,340
 Ne znam da li vi razumijete

427
00:16:47,340 --> 00:16:48,620
 kako to treba načiniti,

428
00:16:48,620 --> 00:16:50,080
 jer vidim da mnogi ne znaju,

429
00:16:50,080 --> 00:16:50,860
 jednostavno ne znaju

430
00:16:50,860 --> 00:16:51,620
 kut bi sa tom

431
00:16:51,620 --> 00:16:52,940
 tabletom

432
00:16:52,940 --> 00:16:53,900
 kojim ja pokažem

433
00:16:53,900 --> 00:16:55,380
 ili kut bi sa tom injekcijom,

434
00:16:55,380 --> 00:16:56,940
 gdje bi bacili van

435
00:16:56,940 --> 00:16:57,560
 ili u usta

436
00:16:57,560 --> 00:16:58,640
 ili u žilu.

437
00:16:58,640 --> 00:17:01,600
 Treba da je točno znat

438
00:17:01,600 --> 00:17:02,280
 kako se to raje.

439
00:17:02,280 --> 00:17:03,580
 Dakle, kad reknem

440
00:17:03,580 --> 00:17:05,500
 ajmo se odlučiti za molitvo.

441
00:17:05,500 --> 00:17:06,740
 Da ti zaista moraš stati,

442
00:17:06,740 --> 00:17:07,620
 mirosec,

443
00:17:07,620 --> 00:17:09,060
 zato ako treba zatvoriti oči,

444
00:17:09,060 --> 00:17:09,740
 reknemš Isuse,

445
00:17:09,740 --> 00:17:11,640
 odlučujem se da ću sad biti s tobom.

446
00:17:11,640 --> 00:17:13,580
 Ili Bože,

447
00:17:13,580 --> 00:17:15,240
 ja sad oću biti s tobom.

448
00:17:15,240 --> 00:17:16,260
 Ti to moraš reći.

449
00:17:16,260 --> 00:17:18,320
 Ne moraš u ustim,

450
00:17:18,320 --> 00:17:19,460
 ali srce,

451
00:17:19,460 --> 00:17:20,480
 tiho u sebi,

452
00:17:20,480 --> 00:17:21,140
 ti to moraš reći.

453
00:17:21,140 --> 00:17:22,160
 Ako to ne kažeš,

454
00:17:22,160 --> 00:17:23,020
 nije se ništo godilo.

455
00:17:23,020 --> 00:17:23,760
 Pazi,

456
00:17:23,760 --> 00:17:25,160
 tek tvoja riječ,

457
00:17:25,260 --> 00:17:26,060
 tvoja odluka.

458
00:17:26,060 --> 00:17:28,920
 Zato pazite da ne bi on sada godilo.

459
00:17:28,920 --> 00:17:29,980
 Da zapišeš sve,

460
00:17:29,980 --> 00:17:30,860
 čuješ sve

461
00:17:30,860 --> 00:17:32,080
 i onda staneš.

462
00:17:32,080 --> 00:17:35,240
 I čekaš dok Ivančeš krene dalje.

463
00:17:35,240 --> 00:17:36,920
 To nije to.

464
00:17:36,920 --> 00:17:39,460
 Ti uzimaš ono što sam rekao,

465
00:17:39,460 --> 00:17:40,820
 tek odnaka ti sam sebi kadaš,

466
00:17:40,820 --> 00:17:42,480
 da, ja se Isuse odlučujem.

467
00:17:42,480 --> 00:17:46,140
 I drugo kad sebi kaže,

468
00:17:46,140 --> 00:17:48,160
 da, ja znam tko sam.

469
00:17:48,160 --> 00:17:49,080
 Ako se moraš reći,

470
00:17:49,080 --> 00:17:50,360
 znam odakle dolazi.

471
00:17:50,360 --> 00:17:52,960
 Ja znam kamo idem.

472
00:17:54,160 --> 00:17:55,960
 Ja znam tko je moja sudbina.

473
00:17:55,960 --> 00:17:58,660
 Nitko ljudi me ne ne pozna.

474
00:17:58,660 --> 00:18:00,840
 Nitko mi ne može spasiti život.

475
00:18:00,840 --> 00:18:02,760
 Nitko mi nije ni dao život.

476
00:18:02,760 --> 00:18:05,880
 Nitko ne zna odakle dolazim na svijet.

477
00:18:05,880 --> 00:18:07,320
 Nitko ne zna šta je to smrt.

478
00:18:07,320 --> 00:18:09,620
 Ima samo jedan koji mi je prijatelj.

479
00:18:09,620 --> 00:18:11,140
 Bog je moj prijatelj.

480
00:18:11,140 --> 00:18:12,280
 I zato znam tko sam.

481
00:18:12,280 --> 00:18:14,760
 I sad si na duhovno razli.

482
00:18:16,200 --> 00:18:18,820
 I treće, baš moraš polako rukom

483
00:18:18,820 --> 00:18:21,700
 i govoriti u ime otca i sina.

484
00:18:21,700 --> 00:18:24,520
 I dok to šapćući govoriš,

485
00:18:24,520 --> 00:18:25,620
 da čuješ gotovo,

486
00:18:25,620 --> 00:18:26,860
 tada se događa.

487
00:18:26,860 --> 00:18:27,460
 Inače ne.

488
00:18:27,460 --> 00:18:32,000
 Znači ćeš ovdje sjediti u saludu.

489
00:18:32,000 --> 00:18:34,420
 Tebi se nudi bogati,

490
00:18:34,420 --> 00:18:35,960
 božanski, nebeski.

491
00:18:37,740 --> 00:18:39,480
 Ovaj okus prekrasnih jela,

492
00:18:39,480 --> 00:18:40,580
 božanskih večera,

493
00:18:40,580 --> 00:18:42,140
 ti ništa nisi okusio.

494
00:18:42,140 --> 00:18:44,260
 I sjediš, prekriženi nogu

495
00:18:44,260 --> 00:18:45,860
 i gledaš, ne znaš kućeš sa sobom.

496
00:18:45,860 --> 00:18:47,340
 Zato moraš obavezno.

497
00:18:47,340 --> 00:18:48,820
 To znači poći,

498
00:18:48,820 --> 00:18:50,140
 kad ti počeš sebi govoriti.

499
00:18:50,140 --> 00:18:55,540
 U ime otca i sina i duha svetoga.

500
00:18:55,540 --> 00:18:56,120
 Amen.

501
00:18:56,120 --> 00:18:57,740
 Da ti se odlučio za Boga.

502
00:18:57,740 --> 00:18:58,640
 Kad ti počeš govoriti,

503
00:18:58,640 --> 00:18:59,640
 ti se odlučio.

504
00:18:59,640 --> 00:19:00,280
 To je tvoja odluka

505
00:19:00,280 --> 00:19:01,200
 i ti za to govoriš.

506
00:19:01,200 --> 00:19:02,900
 Ti izlaziš iz sebe

507
00:19:02,900 --> 00:19:03,680
 i Bogu kažeš da.

508
00:19:03,680 --> 00:19:06,220
 U ime otca i sina i duha svetoga.

509
00:19:07,740 --> 00:19:11,200
 Isto, četvrta točka,

510
00:19:11,200 --> 00:19:11,980
 ti baš moraš reći,

511
00:19:11,980 --> 00:19:14,140
 Isuse, molim da ući.

512
00:19:14,140 --> 00:19:15,440
 I dok to govoriš,

513
00:19:15,440 --> 00:19:16,660
 ti doživljavaš kako tvoja riječ.

514
00:19:16,660 --> 00:19:18,420
 Zajesta, jer je duhovna,

515
00:19:18,420 --> 00:19:19,160
 jer iz tvojega duha,

516
00:19:19,160 --> 00:19:20,260
 prelazi Isusu

517
00:19:20,260 --> 00:19:21,700
 i kako Isusa doziva

518
00:19:21,700 --> 00:19:22,460
 i uvodi u tebe.

519
00:19:22,460 --> 00:19:23,820
 Isus dolazi u tebe.

520
00:19:23,820 --> 00:19:24,840
 Ti to doživljavaš.

521
00:19:24,840 --> 00:19:25,640
 Ako to ne doživljavaš,

522
00:19:25,640 --> 00:19:26,420
 ne moliš kako treba.

523
00:19:26,420 --> 00:19:28,640
 Da dozivljavaš,

524
00:19:28,640 --> 00:19:29,600
 sad si s Isusom.

525
00:19:29,600 --> 00:19:32,700
 To je srce počne drhtati od radosti.

526
00:19:32,700 --> 00:19:34,160
 I za petu točku,

527
00:19:34,200 --> 00:19:35,120
 Isuse, pogledaj se.

528
00:19:35,120 --> 00:19:37,160
 Pogledaj cijeli današnji dan,

529
00:19:37,160 --> 00:19:38,100
 včerašnji dan.

530
00:19:38,100 --> 00:19:40,620
 Pogledaj moji prošli 150 godina,

531
00:19:40,620 --> 00:19:41,880
 30 godina,

532
00:19:41,880 --> 00:19:43,120
 20, 60, 50.

533
00:19:43,120 --> 00:19:44,000
 Pogledaj Isus.

534
00:19:44,000 --> 00:19:45,580
 Samo gledaš za Isusom.

535
00:19:45,580 --> 00:19:46,940
 Kako Isus prvomatra kaže,

536
00:19:46,940 --> 00:19:48,180
 zašto si ovo načinio?

537
00:19:48,180 --> 00:19:50,240
 Zašto nisi ovdje napravio bolje?

538
00:19:50,240 --> 00:19:51,360
 Zašto si se preio?

539
00:19:51,360 --> 00:19:52,880
 Zašto si ovdje psovao?

540
00:19:52,880 --> 00:19:54,420
 A zašto si se poslađao?

541
00:19:54,420 --> 00:19:56,200
 A zašto danas opće nisi molio?

542
00:19:56,200 --> 00:19:58,640
 A zašto jučer opće nisi čitao svetopisima?

543
00:19:58,640 --> 00:20:00,500
 A zašto si došao večeras?

544
00:20:04,200 --> 00:20:06,180
 Samo gledaj Isusa kako on to pregledava,

545
00:20:06,180 --> 00:20:06,980
 tvoje prostore.

546
00:20:06,980 --> 00:20:09,200
 Prostore to je duše

547
00:20:09,200 --> 00:20:12,580
 i kako reagira i kako ti govori.

548
00:20:12,580 --> 00:20:16,600
 Ali kao što si ti govorio Isusu,

549
00:20:16,600 --> 00:20:17,540
 sad on tebi govori,

550
00:20:17,540 --> 00:20:18,180
 to se čuje,

551
00:20:18,180 --> 00:20:19,080
 njegova riječ.

552
00:20:19,080 --> 00:20:20,620
 I ta riječ koju čuješ,

553
00:20:20,620 --> 00:20:21,320
 šta te liječi?

554
00:20:21,320 --> 00:20:23,840
 Njegova riječ.

555
00:20:23,840 --> 00:20:26,980
 Te moraš,

556
00:20:26,980 --> 00:20:27,940
 Isus je riječi,

557
00:20:27,940 --> 00:20:29,340
 bez riječi on ne dolazi.

558
00:20:29,340 --> 00:20:32,260
 I ovo je sve riječi,

559
00:20:32,260 --> 00:20:33,240
 sada moraš riječi,

560
00:20:33,320 --> 00:20:34,380
 govoriti Bogu.

561
00:20:34,380 --> 00:20:37,120
 Odvratite njegovu riječ,

562
00:20:37,120 --> 00:20:38,040
 riječu,

563
00:20:38,040 --> 00:20:39,760
 kada riječ Božja dolazi k tebi.

564
00:20:39,760 --> 00:20:41,180
 A riječ Božja je Bog.

565
00:20:41,180 --> 00:20:45,520
 I onda kad on dobroši,

566
00:20:45,520 --> 00:20:46,360
 ti ga gledaš,

567
00:20:46,360 --> 00:20:47,380
 kadaš da ćeš otići,

568
00:20:47,380 --> 00:20:47,920
 ne Isuse,

569
00:20:47,920 --> 00:20:49,700
 kao Marija Magdalena,

570
00:20:49,700 --> 00:20:50,920
 zagrliću tvoje noge,

571
00:20:50,920 --> 00:20:52,580
 ne dam ti da odeš.

572
00:20:52,580 --> 00:20:54,240
 Ostani Isuse,

573
00:20:54,240 --> 00:20:55,480
 jer ja ću opet biti isti

574
00:20:55,480 --> 00:20:56,480
 koji učer ako odeš.

575
00:20:56,480 --> 00:20:58,340
 Ali to mu reci,

576
00:20:58,340 --> 00:21:00,360
 sad ostani, molim da.

577
00:21:02,440 --> 00:21:04,980
 ostani,

578
00:21:04,980 --> 00:21:05,980
 ti znaš moje muke,

579
00:21:05,980 --> 00:21:07,660
 ti znaš moje bolesti,

580
00:21:07,660 --> 00:21:10,220
 znaš moj pakao,

581
00:21:10,220 --> 00:21:11,120
 kod kuće,

582
00:21:11,120 --> 00:21:12,160
 na faksu,

583
00:21:12,160 --> 00:21:13,440
 poduzeću.

584
00:21:15,360 --> 00:21:16,500
 molim da ostani u meni.

585
00:21:16,500 --> 00:21:22,040
 To je sada uvod u molitu,

586
00:21:22,040 --> 00:21:23,320
 sad si ušao u molitu,

587
00:21:23,320 --> 00:21:25,100
 to kao kad si ušao u more,

588
00:21:25,100 --> 00:21:26,600
 zaronio si,

589
00:21:26,600 --> 00:21:27,400
 sad si u Bogu.

590
00:21:27,400 --> 00:21:28,740
 E, šta sad?

591
00:21:28,740 --> 00:21:30,980
 Sad je na tebi da plivaš.

592
00:21:30,980 --> 00:21:34,080
 Sad je na tebi da se koprcaš,

593
00:21:34,080 --> 00:21:34,780
 da naučiš plivaš.

594
00:21:34,780 --> 00:21:35,980
 Sad ti pitaš Isaka,

595
00:21:35,980 --> 00:21:36,620
 kako je tebi?

596
00:21:36,620 --> 00:21:39,060
 Isuse, šta da rade?

597
00:21:40,220 --> 00:21:41,960
 Isuse, ajmo sada ovim prijateljom

598
00:21:41,960 --> 00:21:42,860
 da ih počnemo voljeti,

599
00:21:42,860 --> 00:21:43,540
 daj baš da vidim

600
00:21:43,540 --> 00:21:44,680
 koji su to ljudi ovdje.

601
00:21:44,680 --> 00:21:46,720
 Jo, Isuse,

602
00:21:46,720 --> 00:21:47,780
 samo nemoj da moram doći

603
00:21:47,780 --> 00:21:48,440
 k njima blizu,

604
00:21:48,440 --> 00:21:49,000
 poludit ću.

605
00:21:49,000 --> 00:21:50,540
 Ja se njih bojim.

606
00:21:50,540 --> 00:21:54,340
 Ti znaš, Isuse,

607
00:21:54,340 --> 00:21:55,440
 da se ja bojim ljudi.

608
00:21:55,440 --> 00:21:56,600
 On kaže,

609
00:21:56,600 --> 00:21:57,900
 ajde, pođi za mnom,

610
00:21:57,900 --> 00:21:58,800
 nemoj ići ispred mene.

611
00:21:58,800 --> 00:21:59,840
 Ajde za mnom.

612
00:21:59,840 --> 00:22:01,580
 Ja ću ti pokazati

613
00:22:01,580 --> 00:22:02,740
 kako je svaki od ljudi

614
00:22:02,740 --> 00:22:03,720
 neizmjerno dobari,

615
00:22:03,720 --> 00:22:04,820
 kako je svaki čezan

616
00:22:04,820 --> 00:22:05,840
 da ti njega voliš.

617
00:22:05,840 --> 00:22:08,880
 I niko ti neće napraviti zlo

618
00:22:08,880 --> 00:22:09,580
 kad ga voliš.

619
00:22:09,580 --> 00:22:12,660
 Pas slaje na tebe

620
00:22:12,660 --> 00:22:14,780
 onda kad se ti njega bojiš.

621
00:22:14,780 --> 00:22:17,160
 A kad ti psu rekneš samo

622
00:22:17,160 --> 00:22:18,160
 o, ti si draki,

623
00:22:18,160 --> 00:22:18,540
 malo,

624
00:22:18,540 --> 00:22:19,060
 on dmah reći,

625
00:22:19,060 --> 00:22:20,400
 čuču, pa prestane.

626
00:22:20,400 --> 00:22:26,040
 Svati, kad ti ideš psu ususred,

627
00:22:26,040 --> 00:22:27,140
 pa podvineš rep

628
00:22:27,140 --> 00:22:27,880
 i gledaš ga,

629
00:22:27,880 --> 00:22:28,720
 onda pas odmah svati,

630
00:22:28,720 --> 00:22:29,560
 onda i on podvine repa,

631
00:22:29,560 --> 00:22:30,620
 wow, wow, wow, wow,

632
00:22:30,620 --> 00:22:31,500
 i skači.

633
00:22:31,500 --> 00:22:33,340
 A kad ti malo mašeš rep,

634
00:22:33,340 --> 00:22:33,700
 on čuču,

635
00:22:33,760 --> 00:22:34,900
 on isto maše rep,

636
00:22:34,900 --> 00:22:36,220
 će ovo i dođe gledat.

637
00:22:36,220 --> 00:22:41,340
 To ti isus kaže,

638
00:22:41,340 --> 00:22:41,620
 dakle,

639
00:22:41,620 --> 00:22:42,960
 tako se ljubi

640
00:22:42,960 --> 00:22:43,800
 druge ljude.

